des:
Mystic Quotes to help you understand what LIFE actually is, what LOVE actually is, what RELATIONSHIP actually is, what EMPATHY actually is and what is the TRUE PURPOSE of your EXISTENCE. 

Just simple yet effective quotes. Nothing else. No "Yes"-"No" question answers, no feedback messages, no distractions. Just quotes.

To listed to Mystic quotes,

Enable the skill and say, "Alexa, open Mystic Quotes"
That's it. Alexa will share one new Mystic quote daily. 

To get help, say, "Alexa, help"

We would love to know about your experience. That is why we ask for your constructive feedback here. Please share your feedback on website or inside Alexa app. We do not ask to provide feedback inside the skill. Remember, "JUST QUOTES"

If you face any issues with skill, please send us an email at support@smartvoicestudio.com
